Inline $a_b$ and \LaTeX{} plus $\alpha$.

\begin{equation}
e^{i\pi}+1=0
\end{equation}
\begin{align}
a &= b + c
\end{align}

See \cite{doe2026,roe2026} on \textit{<2026-05-10 Sun>}.
